description:
Tree works to various trees covered under TPO 86A
 SPLIT DECISION: (1) Approve works to: T131 dead Cherry - fell and grind out stump; T129 Cherry - lift crown to 3m, T108 Lime beside 42 Templewood - fell and grind out stump; T106 multi-stemmed Horse Chestnut by pedestrian gate to Kent Gardens - reduce crown by 30% and reshape
 
 (2) Refuse works to: T119 Lime beside 5 Hardwick Green - Fell and grind out stump to 300mm below ground level; T117 Whitebeam rear of 3/4 Hardwick Green - Reduce crown by 50%, reshape and remove deadwood; T127 Rowan beside 22 Templewood - reduce crown by 50%, reshape and remove deadwood; T130 Cherry - fell and grind out to 300mm
